      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, ensuring a dependable driving experience. While the exterior paint retains a nice shine, there are a few minor surface scratches and small stone chips typical for its age. The interior is clean and comfortable, though you may notice some light wear on the driver's seat bolster.",
