      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant restoration or may serve best as a parts car. The engine currently struggles to turn over and exhibits a noticeable knock, while the transmission slips during gear changes. The exterior shows substantial rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, and the interior upholstery is heavily torn with non-functional electronics. Please expect to invest considerable time and resources into repairs if you intend to make this roadworthy again.",
